{"tid":1641251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】馬鞍山新港城4男1女保安涉阻差辦公被捕","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:51:04.000Z","uid":329581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"393d7659295cb418b0d3f4ded7ed66dcda652283","tid":1641251,"uid":329581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191009&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60134401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191009%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60134401&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=c2f15f9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191009%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60134401&h=12a4e154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191009&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60134401</a> <br />\n<br />\n周一晚防暴警於多區進行搜捕行動時，馬鞍山新港城中心曾有商場保安盡力頂住大門，惟最終在警方暴力下終失守，警方昨於記者會中辯稱因要通過商場前往另一端，故在無辦法的情況下推開大門進入商場。消息指4男1女保安於周一晚因拒絕防暴警進入商場，涉嫌阻差辦公被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據當日傳媒直播片段拍到，周一晚上約9時49分，多名防暴警圖闖入馬鞍山新港城，3名男保安及1名女保安員於商場門口頂住大門，阻止防暴警進入，另外亦約3名保安員在調停，突然其中一道門被防暴警推開，保安員視線轉向該名突圍的防暴警，其他警員乘勢一同闖入商場，並於商場內將多人壓倒在地上。其間有一名保安員張開雙臂圖阻止警員但就被推開，另外亦有警員推跌《立場新聞》女記者，更疑試圖將她壓在地上，另一名警員隨即制止並提醒該名警員她是記者。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》女記者其後坐起，並直指推跌她的防暴警，指控他將其眼鏡撥走，並用胡椒噴霧指向她，又扯走了她的手機充電線。最終另一名防暴警將她扶起。隨後警方離開商場收隊，多名圍觀市民不滿，紛紛指罵警員。"},{"pid":"44be38aacedc151cc2c169092e69a9d0dfe801c3","tid":1641251,"uid":329581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a086d0f4b523358c067d977a69ced962de0a8bb0","tid":1641251,"uid":329581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"【17:38】據了解，有仍然當值的保安表示，被捕5名保安今午3時半準時上班，其後其上司指示5人自行前往馬鞍山警署，相信5人是抵達警署後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191009/s00001/1570612157795/%e9%a6%ac%e9%9e%8d%e5%b1%b1%e6%96%b0%e6%b8%af%e5%9f%8e%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%89%e9%98%bb%e8%ad%a6%e7%a1%ac%e9%97%96-%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1-5%e4%ba%ba%e6%b6%89%e9%98%bb%e5%b7%ae%e8%be%a6%e5%85%ac%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191009%2Fs00001%2F1570612157795%2F%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e9%259e%258d%25e5%25b1%25b1%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%259f%258e%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%25ae%2589%25e9%2598%25bb%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%25a1%25ac%25e9%2597%2596-%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1-5%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%2598%25bb%25e5%25b7%25ae%25e8%25be%25a6%25e5%2585%25ac%25e4%25bb%258a%25e6%2597%25a9%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=57ae465f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191009%2Fs00001%2F1570612157795%2F%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e9%259e%258d%25e5%25b1%25b1%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%259f%258e%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%25ae%2589%25e9%2598%25bb%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%25a1%25ac%25e9%2597%2596-%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1-5%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%2598%25bb%25e5%25b7%25ae%25e8%25be%25a6%25e5%2585%25ac%25e4%25bb%258a%25e6%2597%25a9%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&h=44f36dd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191009/s00001/1570612157795/%e9%a6%ac%e9%9e%8d%e5%b1%b1%e6%96%b0%e6%b8%af%e5%9f%8e%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%89%e9%98%bb%e8%ad%a6%e7%a1%ac%e9%97%96-%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1-5%e4%ba%ba%e6%b6%89%e9%98%bb%e5%b7%ae%e8%be%a6%e5%85%ac%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95</a>"}]}